data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!  Come HOME to this nature lovers dream in Ocean Springs!  On almost a half acre double lot, this unique 3 bedroom, 2 bath, split floorplan home in Gulf Park Estates features high ceilings in the living room with a propane fireplace.  The 2nd bedroom could easily be another living room or den, another primary OR the perfect in-law suite. There's even a bonus room upstairs from it perfect for crafting, gaming, storage or even bird watching!  Stainless steel appliances all stay, as well as the washer and dryer. The Solar Panels are paid for, and offer you huge saving on your monthly power bills! There's even a man cave/she shed out back with power & window A/C.  Situated just minutes from downtown Ocean Springs, you'll have easy access to dining, shopping, and entertainment. Don't miss this chance for tranquility - schedule your tour today and have this new home for the holidays! Sellers are offering a 1 yr home warranty to new homeowners at closing. Agents - Be sure to read Agent Remarks.
